      <div class="main__content">
        <h1> THAILAND TOURIST TRAVELS</h1>
        <h2> Let's explore the unexplored </h2>
        <div class="main__img--container">
          <img src="/images/homepagepic.svg" alt="pic" id="main__img" />
        </div>

        <div class="container-fluid">
          <p>Welcome {{user.NAME}}</p> <!-- The name of the user that logged in is extracted from the database and displayed on screen-->
         
        </div>


        <div class="main2">
          <p class="p1"> ABOUT:</p>
          <p class="p2"> <br> TTT is a simple website created to provide tourists withbasic information
          which could assist to decide if to plan a trip to Thailand . And if there is already a plan to go visit Thailand then this website 
          would be helpful to prepare for the trip.
        



          </p>

          <p class="p3"> <br> Thailand is an exceptionnaly beautiful country and worth
            a visit not only once but multiple times, because you never
            get bored of it. It provides a wide range of places to be
            discovered, and is not only wonderful for an experience
            of city life in its capital Bangkok but also full of
            different aspects of natures from blue beaches to green rocky
            mountains,there is nothing left out.
          </p>

          <p class="p4"> <br>This website gives an idea of the  places that could be visited in  Thailand, by listing the three 
          most visited and liked cities : Bangkok,phuket and pattaya , the details on the famous things to do in these cities
           are shown , and 
          an estimation on the expenses for one person in one day is also provided ,which would indicate to the traveller if the trip is in 
          their budget 
          and worth their time. 
          <br>A currency converter is available on the services page to enable users to directly convert the estimations shown in baht , thai currency,
          to their own currency , making it easier to understand the budget required without the need of switching pages to search, giving
          the users a smooth experience.
          <br>A weather service is also available, which is a tool provided for  the users to search for the weather in the different citites
          in Thaialnd to help them know the weather conditions there and be prepared with appropriate clothes to pack,
           and if curious the users could serach for any city in this world on this free tool to know its weather , either for comparison or 
           even just for  fun! 
            <br>

          </p>
